reviews.review_text:
if this isn't a five star performance, what is? An absolutely legendary recording. 

The first set is excellent. 

The second set is one of the greatest of all time, and was used in the recording of Anthem of the Sun. 

Alligator is a masterpiece. 

Keep a copy of this one stowed away for the Time Capsule. A TOP 10 all-time Grateful Dead performance, if there ever was one...
